---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import CF from '../../components/Confetti.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Confetti"
  description="Celebratory particle burst that can be triggered by hover or click."
>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p class="text-base text-slate-100">
      Confetti renders a canvas-based celebration animation that you can trigger
      via user action or programmatically. The component respects the user's
      reduced-motion preference and exposes events for programmatic control.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Props</h2>
    <dl class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          autoStart?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Start the animation automatically when rendered. Defaults to <code
            >false</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          duration?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Duration in ms for the confetti animation. Defaults to <code
            >2000</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          particleCount?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Number of particles created. Defaults to <code>160</code>.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          colors?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Array of color hex values used for particles. Defaults to a
          theme-aware set.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Usage</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Render the component inside any container. Provide <code>autoStart</code> to
      run immediately or omit it and render the built-in trigger button for manual
      control. The component emits custom events (<code>confetti:start</code>, <code
        >confetti:stop</code
      >, <code>confetti:burst</code>).
    </p>
    <pre
      class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-slate-700/70 bg-slate-950/80 p-4 text-sm text-slate-50 shadow-inner">
      <code class="language-astro">{`<Confetti />`}</code>
    </pre>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Example</h2>
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
      <PageHeader
        title="Milestone unlocked"
        subtitle="Ship a celebratory confetti effect when the user reaches key goals."
      />
      <div class="mt-4">
        <CF />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Accessibility</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Canvas is hidden from assistive technology (<code>aria-hidden</code>)
      since the effect is decorative. The trigger button is accessible, labeled,
      keyboard-focusable, and uses a clear focus ring. The component respects <code
        >prefers-reduced-motion</code
      > and will not animate when reduced motion is enabled.
    </p>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
